{"tid":1395786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民作「元朗國歌」諷白衣人","createTime":"2019-08-02T00:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T01:04:04.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dbfa4e0ace1cea0c6ad7e7f7ad227c385e69f44d","tid":1395786,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:54:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190802/s00002/1564684858283/%e3%80%90emily%e3%80%91%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8c%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e5%9c%8b%e6%ad%8c%e3%80%8d%e8%ab%b7%e7%99%bd%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190802%2Fs00002%2F1564684858283%2F%25e3%2580%2590emily%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591%25e4%25bd%259c%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%25ad%258c%25e3%2580%258d%25e8%25ab%25b7%25e7%2599%25bd%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e4%25ba%25ba&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFMwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=d93828c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190802%2Fs00002%2F1564684858283%2F%25e3%2580%2590emily%25e3%2580%2591%25e7%25b6%25b2%25e6%25b0%2591%25e4%25bd%259c%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e5%259c%258b%25e6%25ad%258c%25e3%2580%258d%25e8%25ab%25b7%25e7%2599%25bd%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e4%25ba%25ba&h=c7ca46ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190802/s00002/1564684858283/%e3%80%90emily%e3%80%91%e7%b6%b2%e6%b0%91%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8c%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e5%9c%8b%e6%ad%8c%e3%80%8d%e8%ab%b7%e7%99%bd%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190802/s00046/10e2af42c6ac0c865f79905391ea4bce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190802%2Fs00046%2F10e2af42c6ac0c865f79905391ea4bce.jpg&h=64b6ddeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】元朗7．21白衣人襲擊市民事件引起全城關注，立法會議員何君堯形容施襲者係「保家衛族」，備受批評。網民不時諷刺元朗已「獨立」，笑言去元朗要申請簽證；近日就有網民將國歌改詞，改寫成由粵語唱出嘅《元朗人民共和國國歌》（圖），第一句就係「元朗！建設這何氏大帝國！」，另有「全力應對挑戰！萬民手執起竹棍，元朗！」，以歌詞批評元朗部分人已經自成一國，可以無視香港法律咁話。<br />\n笑言去元朗要申請簽證<br />\n<br />\n呢首「元朗國歌」，頭幾句係「元朗！建設這何氏大帝國！是無懼六鄉村，衛族群力保家建國！鄉鎮同力保衛村落唱起這歌，無盡勇氣未懼軍警死守於祠堂」。去到歌曲中後段激昂位置，網民就「曲線」話元朗要建國，並諷刺白衣人拎起竹棍打人：「元朗！建家！立邦！全力應對挑戰！萬民手執起竹棍，元朗！萬民手執起竹棍，元朗！元朗，元朗，大帝國！」<br />\n<br />\n有網民話恭喜元朗「終於獨立成國」，又高呼「元朗人民共和國主席何君堯萬歲」；有人話市民日後去元朗，記得要向白衣人申請簽證。有人笑言《國歌法》本地立法後，呢首國歌就會變禁歌，但亦有元朗居民對事件感到傷心，話對呢首改歌「笑唔出」。"},{"pid":"ad876a9860eeede6e0872ecfb2742822d7e68f70","tid":1395786,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}